Executive: Ya sir voice pe baat karte, toh aawaz aayegi na aapko.

Executive: Thik hai voice pe baat karte, thik hai.
Customer: Nahi nahi aawaz nahi aayi, aawaz nahi aayi, phone me baat kijiye, aawaz nahi aayi.
Executive: Toh ek second sir main aapko direct call karta hu, ek minute dekhiyega bas.
Customer: Haan haan thik hai.
